description: Demolition of rear parts of the existing Town Hall Building; retention / refurbishment of frontage building with continued A2, B1 and D1 uses, demolition of the existing Clyde Road Depot buildings, including existing bunker, (retaining central part of South Range Building) and erection of 4 blocks of houses / flats between 3 and 5 storeys comprising 109 units, associated landscaping, car parking and means of access.
